                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for optimizing mixing of various reducing gases in hydrogen-rich carbon circulating oxygen blast furnace",
                    "富氢碳循环氧气高炉优化掺混多种还原性气体的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a method for optimally mixing various reducing gases in a hydrogen-rich carbon circulating oxygen blast furnace, which is characterized in that natural gas including coke oven gas does not pass through a gas heating furnace and is used as mixed gas obtained by heating decarburized gas of the hydrogen-rich carbon circulating oxygen blast furnace. The addition of coke oven gas and natural gas at a low-temperature end is upgraded into the addition at a high-temperature section, so that the hydrogen-rich gas can be sprayed into the furnace to participate in reduction by increasing the temperature without passing through a gas heating furnace; meanwhile, the defects that solution foaming is caused when natural gas passes through a decarburization system, hydrogen-rich gas H2 in coke oven gas reacts with SiO2 in refractory materials after passing through a gas heating furnace, and the performance of the refractory materials is degraded are overcome."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种富氢碳循环氧气高炉优化掺混多种还原性气体的方法，将天然气包括焦炉煤气不经过煤气加热炉，用于富氢碳循环氧气高炉的脱碳煤气加热后的混合煤气使用，本发明改变了掺混的配入方式，使焦炉煤气、天然气由煤气低温端的配入升级为高温段的配入，从而实现富氢气体不经过煤气加热炉也可提高温度喷入炉内参与还原的作用，同时也避免了天然气通过脱碳系统引起溶液发泡以及焦炉煤气中富氢气体H2通过煤气加热炉后与耐材中的SiO2反应，降解耐材的性能的弊端。"
                }
            ]
        }
